==票房與評價==
本片於1992年12月11日起在1,925個戲院上映，頭一週的票房收入為1,551萬7,468美元，之後三週內的票房也都蟬聯第一。最後的全球累積收入為2億365萬美元，包括美國票房的1億4,134萬又178美元，和海外票房的9,515萬又9,822美元<ref>{{cite web|title=A Few Good Men- box office data|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movies/1992/0FGME.php|publisher=Nash Information Services, LLC.|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2011-09-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110908155555/http://the-numbers.com/movies/1992/0FGME.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

而除了票房之外，本片在影評方面也獲得很大的成功<ref>{{cite news|title=`A Few Good Men' Outpaces 2 Biographic Openings|work=Chicago Tribune|date=1993-01-01|url=http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1993-01-01/entertainment/9303152126_1_location-million-for-seventh-place-weeks|accessdate=2010-10-26|first=John|last=Horn|archive-date=2011-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110916151935/http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1993-01-01/entertainment/9303152126_1_location-million-for-seventh-place-weeks|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Weekend Box Office `Aladdin's' Magic Carpet Ride|work=Los Angeles Times|date=1993-01-26|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1993-01-26/entertainment/ca-2081_1_weekend-box-office|accessdate=2010-11-18|first=David J.|last=Fox|archive-date=2012-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120309193603/http://articles.latimes.com/1993-01-26/entertainment/ca-2081_1_weekend-box-office|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[滾石雜誌|滾石雜誌]]》的彼得·崔佛斯（{{lang|en|Peter Travers}}）說「本片均一的傑出表現該歸功於洛·雷納，他進行了巧妙的執導、結合了懸疑和角色，來塑造出一部強力撼動人心的電影」<ref>{{cite web|title=Rotten Tomatoes- A Few Good Men review|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/few_good_men/comments.php?reviewid=221143|publisher=Flixster Inc.|accessdate=2011-06-22}}</ref>{{ref label|Travers|註1|}}。《[[時代雜誌|時代雜誌]]》的理查·史柴寇（{{lang|en|Richard Schickel}}）稱本片為「一部優秀的好電影，在敘述這個稀鬆平常、但又引人入勝的劇情時，沒有任何浪費的台詞或畫面」<ref>{{cite news|last=Schickel|first=Richard|title=Close-Order Moral Drill|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,977216-1,00.html|work=Time Monday, Dec. 14, 1992|publisher=Time, Inc.|accessdate=2011-06-22|date=1992-12-14|archive-date=2012-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121107110601/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,977216-1,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{ref label|Schickel|註2|}}。《[[綜藝|綜藝]]》週刊的陶德·麥卡錫（{{lang|en|Todd McCarthy}}）則預料「這道吸引了劇院內普羅觀眾目光的戲劇性火花，對於影迷們而言將會更加地難以抗拒，因為它具有出色的力量」<ref>{{cite news|last=McCarthy|first=Todd|title=A Few Good Men- Review|url=http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117900056?refcatid=31|publisher=RBI, a division of Reed Elsevier Inc.|accessdate=2011-06-22|date=1992-11-12|archive-date=2012-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120112191745/http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117900056?refcatid=31|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{ref label|McCarthy|註3|}}。

本片在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上得到了81%的評比<ref>{{cite web|title=Rotten Tomatoes- A Few Good Men|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/few_good_men|publisher=Flixster Inc.|accessdate=2011-06-22|archive-date=2011-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111030013537/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/few_good_men/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

